column5: Any reports of your trip out of Nakina?

Yea their hasn't been much here so far this year on the nakina camps I think other than yous maybe one other. Was wondering about water levels, bugs etc. as were headed to Mellchet in 12 days. will contact you when we get back. haven't forgotten about later in the year fishing Info for Mellchet. ........................Halfmoon
Come on!!!! Someone has to fly out of Nakina to a favorite lake. Take a few minutes and reply to this. What was your experience???
I would, but we're not headed up to Meta for another two weeks!
We didn't fly out of Nakina but were very close to some of the fly out lakes, fishing was the best year yet with lots of 20" plus fish.https://youtu.be/S46C8qbNKtw
I posted on a trip into Kayedon. Fishing was excellent.
